a Professor of Neurobiology

00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:14.770
and Ophthalmology at
Stanford School of Medicine.

00:00:14.770 --> 00:00:17.060
Today, we're going to talk
all about how to optimize

00:00:17.060 --> 00:00:19.890
your workspace for maximum productivity.

00:00:19.890 --> 00:00:22.810
Indeed, that means to
heighten levels of focus,

00:00:22.810 --> 00:00:25.110
to increase levels of creativity,

00:00:25.110 --> 00:00:27.510
to improve your ability to task switch.

00:00:27.510 --> 00:00:30.020
